>\n但開始覺得有啲夾硬為講而講<br />\n由其啲絲打投稿好假"},{"pid":"86752e240e759ba57a356fef42e00f06c07d4de8","tid":314581,"uid":47797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T19:34:34.000Z","msg":"應承我做某樣嘢﹐應承十次都無次做到﹐屌鳩翻我轉頭。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35f7a7d1d884d33da43f75b81dde1e3bec58df91","tid":314581,"uid":47797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T19:37:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>扮嬲點知真係嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我嬲 佢氹唔到我 點知佢嬲咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nSame here<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff70a4c21d56613fb8d6f6864b3783001a4d5478","tid":314581,"uid":47699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T19:39:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>大部分女仔都好自卑<br />\n我成日笑我女朋友好肥 但其實佢babyfat<br />\n有次玩大咗 話佢肥到欣宜咁 佢忍唔住喊<br />\n之後比我知道佢偷偷地節食跑步<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好彩阻止到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係咁逼佢食翻野<br />\n<br />\n利申：佢得46kg我覺得有啲肉地好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢真係好愛你<br />\nso sweet"},{"pid":"ad418fe65cf86e541423876381204857d2ca3741","tid":314581,"uid":47699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T19:40:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實女仔發脾氣係咩心態，成日無嗱嗱發脾氣好煩，問佢咩事又話唔知，你唔知我點知啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有時係因為佢嬲嬲下 會嬲埋自己小氣<br />\n又唔想你覺得佢咁小事都嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"998228bc77adf49dca46fe9f8c389ec729914513","tid":314581,"uid":44704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T19:41:24.000Z","msg":"同佢講道理"},{"pid":"0e9642f8ecabf2a5622671fac04dfd8c586457b6","tid":314581,"uid":126841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T19:41:50.000Z","msg":"我話我自己蠢俾佢嬲咗成晚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07dd18940793953dbdd08df4c3e909b7acf14a8d","tid":314581,"uid":50574,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T19:52:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有冇人係因為個女朋友自卑所以發脾氣？例如話佢肥，蠢，胸平所以就嬲咗？</blockquote><br />\n我男朋友就係呢d仆街!你地睇下自己咩樣先啦,講一二次就講笑姐,日日講真係火那滾,你咁介意咪分手囉,一d都唔理人感受</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係男都覺得on9，唔知講呢d黎做乜鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  有冇諗過條女係唔想俾自己男朋友話而唔係自卑，hurt左人仲話人自卑，on9冇藥醫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea301027bee84f9bbaeade615541f848fd292042","tid":314581,"uid":32500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T21:24:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>佢之前男朋友鍾意同佢玩毒龍鑽 搞到佢都鍾意埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nHehe?"},{"pid":"698f164389527c1d2f9c0db6be4c64c063245523","tid":314581,"uid":40737,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T22:09:48.000Z","msg":"咀佢個陣話我個嘴脣冇熱嬲鳩<br />\n<br />\n估佢想講咩估唔岩之後鳩嬲<br />\n<br />\n傾電話個陣佢無啦啦打鳩斷我，講左句「我愛你」，之後有反問我點解唔早佢一步講「我愛你」之後嬲<br />\n<br />\n有次見面個陣佢遲到，我邊用手機邊等佢，佢無啦啦背後彈出黎嚇鳩我，我俾佢當堂嚇左一跳，呆左幾秒，你地知唔知佢今次嬲咩啊？ 嬲鳩我見到佢冇感到好撚驚喜啊屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d52a8b19ba56f1e0f017e2a23b7edb2973e7e76c","tid":314581,"uid":126766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T22:17:35.000Z","msg":"因為我9up話女仔長頭髮係正常<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢短頭髮"},{"pid":"f126a73bd02b8d369a80638caa0f5746e1185754","tid":314581,"uid":103889,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T22:22:09.000Z","msg":"男可以嗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我生日